description:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Heyo RWR-community,

Here is a small tool which allows you to be informed when one of the listed online servers reaches an amount of minimum players you set. Once this number of players is reached, you will be informed visually (trayicon will turn green and there will be a tooltip poping up) and and audible alert will be played.
You can configure the minimum number of players that you want by right-clicking the tray icon with some more settings coming along.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*How to Install*
Extract the 4 files into main game directory/folder.

^^^^Common Example: C:Program Files (x86)Running with Rifles^^^^^

